==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irresolution
<hw>Ir*res`o*lu"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>irr⟦eacute⟧solution</ets>.]</ety> <def>Lack of resolution; lack of
decision in purpose; a fluctuation of mind, as in doubt, or between hope
and fear; irresoluteness; indecision; vacillation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Irresolution</qex> on the schemes of life which offer
themselves to our choice, and inconstancy in pursuing them, are the
greatest causes of all unhappiness.</q> <rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irresolvability</ent>⟦br⟧
